notes:
Call 218-435-1000 for an appointment. Walk-ins are also welcome!
The Pharmacy is giving Moderna, Pfizer and Johnson & Johnson vaccines.
Moderna and Pfizer requires a second shot in 28/21 days. Johnson & Johnson does not require a second shot.
We try to offer all 3 for your convenience.
Hours and days may vary and brands of vaccinations are subject to change with the state allocation process.
